text: Feeling some type of wayI m not quite sure what it is I m doing or supposed to be doing anymore  My depression used to be very aggressive  but these days I don t even feel it  really  Just the big empty now  In a way it is better  not feeling the rage and despair  but in other ways it is not  I also don t feel love  happiness  the other things I used to be able to describe but just can t seem to remember anymore The biggest disappointment was that getting clean did not help  They all swore that that was my problem  Too much pot  Too much LSD  Too many cigarettes  Well  I don t know what else to say now except that being sober is a bummer  Being high wasn t healthy  yeah  but at least I lived in a different world all the time   Where do you look that you don t see either the most absurd levels of excess  whether it be material  violence  hatred  or ridiculousness  or emptiness  At least for what I ve been looking for  the world is empty  There is no place to lay my head and forget about the very serious nonsense we ve surrounded ourselves with  There is no time to think about the beauty of what is when we are constantly throwing ourselves at what could  should  might  won t  can t  and will be later on   And on top of it all  I got married in January  This is literally the best time of my life and it s just  nothing  I don t know what kind of husband that makes me but I can assume not a great one  She wants to have a baby  I don t even know how to describe how confusing that is to me  I d never wish life on another being  let alone purposely  But it seems to be my fate  Either that or I disappoint the only person who has ever really helped me feel less bad about being me by not being me anymore   I don t know that this made any sense  I don t know that I really said anything at all  I can only imagine what reading this is like and for those of you who do  sorry  For everything and nothing and whatever lays in between
summary: Getting clean did not help the depression. Being sober is a bummer. Being high wasn't healthy but at least I lived in a different world all the time. He got married in January. His wife wants to have a baby and he doesn't know what to do.
